  "title": "[Gov Healthcare] Executive Assistant, Medical Records Officer -UP$3200 @WEST #HCY",
  "description": "<p><p><strong>Scanning and Record Management </strong><br /></p><p><br />Check case note folders to ensure accuracy and completeness of medical records</p><p>Update medical records movement promptly in the Medical Records Management System (MRMS) for easy retrieval</p><p>Ensure all thin charts (loose notes) from clinics and wards are scanned within 24 hours of receipt</p><p>Conduct quality checks on scanned and indexed records in accordance with scanning guidelines</p><p>File medical records pending scanning according to established procedures for easy retrieval</p><p>Maintain proper housekeeping of the medical records library</p><p>Update year codes on medical records folders for future archival</p><p>Answer phone calls from clinics, wards, and departments and follow up on enquiries<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br />Min GCE A levels or Diploma in any discipline<br /></p><p>For interested candidates, please send your most recent and updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:recruithealthcare@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>sallytsin@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a></p><p>WA me at <a href=\"http://wa.me/+6598326219\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://wa.me/+6598326219</a> or tele me at @sallytsin</p><p>Tsin Chien Yee Sally<br />R25127272<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA License No. 99C4599<a href=\"mailto:recruithealthcare@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p></p>",
